header.gameNote: NEW YORK LIFE ACC MEN'S TOURNAMENT - QUARTERFINAL

videos.description: Virginia Tech guad Ahmed Hill intercepts a pass and breaks away to the basket for the easy finish.
videos.headline: Hokies' Hill converts steal into easy layup

videos.description: Florida State guard Terance Mann wraps a pass around a defender to guard M.J. Walker, who knocks down a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Seminoles' Mann finds Walker in the corner for 3-pointer

videos.description: Florida State forward Mfiondu Kabengele denies Virginia Tech guard Wabissa Bede at the rim and Terance Mann finishes with a layup at the other end.
videos.headline: Kabengele's block leads to Seminoles layup at other end

videos.description: Virginia Tech guard Nickeil Alexander-Walker bounces a pass to forward Kerry Blackshear Jr., who rises up for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Blackshear's dunk gives Hokies first lead of the game

videos.description: Florida State guard Devin Vassell pulls up from the corner and knocks down a 3-pointer to send the game to overtime.
videos.headline: Seminoles' Vassell sends game to overtime with 3-pointer

videos.description: Florida State guard Terance Mann drives downcourt and sinks a game-winning jumper with 1.8 seconds left in overtime.
videos.headline: Seminoles' Mann sinks go-ahead jumper in OT
